messages.text: I really miss you.
I miss you more :)
Why can’t I ever come see you again?
Bc my parents don’t want me to have a bf...
So you can’t tell them about us?
They’d probably take away my phone and laptop
And then I’d never get to talk to you!
And we wouldn’t be able to arrange our secret dates ;)
We’d have to resort to carrier pigeons, huh?
Something along those lines.
I really wish I could see you tonight
My dad and mom are fighting again
I hate hearing them yell at each other
I’m sry to hear that :(
What if you tell your parents...
you’re going to Laurie’s?
And then I could pick you up there
and we can go somewhere?
My parents wouldn’t let me out this late...
It’s only 11!
It’s not like 3 in the morning
I know!
But my parents are really strict.
It’s terrible...
Can I see you tomorrow?
I wish.
Grandparents are coming over.
Parents never let me skip out on those visits.
What about later?
They always sleep over =/
How about once they go to sleep?
Old people go to bed early, right?
I’m still not allowed out.
My parents are afraid I might wake them up if I come in too late
Do your parents ever go away for a weekend?
HA and leave me by myself?
Good one. I would love that kind of freedom.
When do your parents go to bed?
They’re both asleep.
So...you could sneak out?
uhhhhh
well...
no.
aww why not?
There’s an alarm on the doors...at night.
And idk the code...so it’ll go off and wake them up.
Man, your parents have you locked up good and tight.
One more year until college.
They’re going to let you go somewhere far?
If I get a full ride somewhere they can’t turn it down.
Got my eye on the west coast!
An expensive plane ride away and a time difference.
Haha nice!
I was looking at a few schools in Cali...
Maybe we’ll be close to each other :)
Is there an alarm on the windows?
No...just the doors.
So someone could climb out your window?
In theory...
But idk how sturdy the tree is by my window =/
And a broken leg because I climbed out the window won’t make things any easier.
Well...
What if I don’t mind risking a broken leg?
You mean...you’re going to drive to my place and climb up a tree to then climb through my window?
If you’re up for it :D
But what if you fall and my parents wake up?
I’ll be as quiet as a church mouse ;)
I don’t know if this is a good idea...
Then when will I see you again :(
School? We barely get to be alone together then
I know =/
It’s just if we risk things now, then I may never get to see you again...or seeing you will be even more difficult than it already is!
It definitely is difficult. But seeing you is worth it every time.
Thank you Josh I really do miss you.
I miss you a lot too.
Maybe another night?
Sure.
I’m going to sleep then.
You’re not going to stay up and text me? :(
Well I’m tired...and the more we talk the more I’m going to want to see you and I might do something stupid that you don’t want me to do.
Well then maybe you should do something stupid ;)
What are you saying?
I’m saying come over!
I want to see you...so badly. And I know you want to see me.
What’s life without a little risk? ;)
Savannah I cannot wait to see you
You’re the best! This won’t be a night either one of us forgets!
I’ll be over in a 15 minutes.
I’ll text you when I’m here!
Drive safe!
Can’t wait :)
a few minutes later
Hey I’m here!
YAY!
Do you see the tree?
Yeah I do
OK the window directly above the tree is mine.
You think you can climb it?
I’ve done rock climbing before.
Plus I’ve got you for added motivation ;)
Hehe it’s like a spin on Rapunzel...instead of my hair, you’ll climb the tree.
To release you from your tower!
Here I go!
OK! I’m getting changed!
Hey wait I don’t see you...
Are you at the right house?
Josh stop climbing!
JOSH!
JOSH WHERE ARE YOU
Answer your window silly :p
I’m at my window...
Where are you?
YOU CLIMBED THE WRONG TREE
YOU DIDN’T TELL ME THERE’S MORE THAN ONE TREE
THE TREE IN THE FRONT LEADS TO MY PARENT’S ROOM
YOU SHOULD HAVE MENTIONED THAT
two weeks later
My parents put locks on the windows now =/
Guess it was a night they didn’t forget...
